\c 29
\s Ukubusa kukaHezekhiya
\p
\v 1 UHezekhiya waba yinkosi eleminyaka engamatshumi amabili lanhlanu; wabusa iminyaka engamatshumi amabili lesificamunwemunye eJerusalema\x + 2 Kho. 18.1-3.\x*. Lebizo likanina lalinguAbhiya indodakazi kaZekhariya\x + 26.5. Isa. 8.2.\x*.
\v 2 Wasesenza okuqondileyo emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* njengokwenza konke kukaDavida uyise.
\p
\v 3 Yena, ngomnyaka wokuqala wokubusa kwakhe ngenyanga yokuqala, wavula iminyango yendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*, wayilungisa\x + 28.24. 29.7.\x*.
\v 4 Wasengenisa abapristi lamaLevi, wababuthanisa egumeni elingasempumalanga.
\v 5 Wasesithi kubo: Ngilalelani, maLevi; khathesi zingcweliseni, njalo lingcwelise indlu yeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu waboyihlo, likhuphe ingcekeza endaweni engcwele\x + 29.15,34. 35.6.\x*.
\v 6 Ngoba obaba babephambukile, benza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu, bayitshiya, baphendula ubuso babo bebususa endaweni yokuhlala yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 35.22. Jer. 2.27. Hez. 8.16.\x*, bafulathela\f + \fk bafulathela: \fl Heb. \fq bapha intamo.\f*.
\v 7 Bavala leminyango yekhulusi, bacitsha izibane, kabatshisanga impepha, kabanikelanga umnikelo wokutshiswa kuNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli\x + 28.24.\x* endaweni engcwele.
\v 8 Ngakho ulaka lweN\nd kosi\nd* lwaba phezu kukaJuda leJerusalema, yabanikela evalweni\x + 24.18.\x*, ekuchithekeni, lekuncifelweni, njengoba libona ngamehlo enu\x + Jer. 19.8. 25.9,18. 29.18. Mika 6.16. Hlu. 5.16. 1 Kho. 9.8. Jer. 18.16. Lilo 2.15.\x*.
\v 9 Ngoba khangelani, obaba bawile ngenkemba, lamadodana ethu lamadodakazi ethu labomkethu basekuthunjweni ngenxa yalokhu\x + 28.5,6,8,17.\x*.
\v 10 Khathesi kusenhliziyweni yami\x + 24.4. 1 Lan. 22.7.\x* ukwenza isivumelwano leN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, ukuze ukuvutha kolaka lwayo kuphenduke kusuke kithi\x + 15.12.\x*.
\v 11 Madodana ami, khathesi lingonwabi, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ilikhethile ukuthi lime phambi kwayo, liyikhonze\x + Nani 3.6. 8.14. 18.2,6. Nani 16.40.\x*, libe zinceku zayo labatshisi bempepha.
\p
\v 12 Asesukuma amaLevi, oMahathi indodana kaAmasayi\x + 31.13,15.\x* loJoweli indodana kaAzariya emadodaneni amaKohathi\x + 34.12. Nani 3.17. 1 Lan. 6.1.\x*; lemadodaneni kaMerari\x + 34.12. Nani 3.17. 1 Lan. 6.1.\x* oKishi indodana kaAbidi\x + 1 Lan. 6.44.\x* loAzariya indodana kaJehaleleli\x + 31.13,15.\x*; lakumaGerishoni\x + 34.12. Nani 3.17. 1 Lan. 6.1.\x* oJowa indodana kaZima\x + 1 Lan. 6.20,21.\x* loEdeni indodana kaJowa\x + 31.13,15.\x*;
\v 13 lemadodaneni kaElizafani oShimiri loJehiyeli\x + 1 Lan. 15.8. Nani 3.30.\x*; lemadodaneni kaAsafi oZekhariya loMathaniya\x + 1 Lan. 6.39.\x*;
\v 14 lemadodaneni kaHemani\x + 1 Lan. 6.33,44.\x* oJehiyeli\x + 31.13,15.\x* loShimeyi\x + 31.13,15.\x*; lemadodaneni kaJeduthuni\x + 1 Lan. 6.33,44.\x* oShemaya loUziyeli\x + 31.13,15.\x*.
\v 15 Basebebuthanisa abafowabo, bazingcwelisa, beza njengomlayo wenkosi ngamazwi kaJehova\x + 29.5,34.\x*, ukuhlanza indlu kaJehova\x + Neh. 13.9.\x*.
\v 16 Abapristi basebengena ngaphakathi kwendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd* uku\add yi\add*hlanza, bakhupha konke ukungcola abakuthola ethempelini leN\nd kosi\nd* egumeni lendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*; lamaLevi akuthatha, akukhuphela esifuleni iKidroni ngaphandle\x + 2 Sam. 15.23.\x*.
\v 17 Basebeqala ukungcwelisa ngolokuqala lwenyanga yokuqala, njalo ngosuku lwesificaminwembili lwenyanga bafika ekhulusini leN\nd kosi\nd*; bangcwelisa indlu yeN\nd kosi\nd* ngensuku eziyisificaminwembili; kwathi ngosuku lwetshumi lesithupha lwenyanga yokuqala baqeda\x + 29.3.\x*.
\v 18 Basebengena phakathi kuHezekhiya inkosi bathi: \add Se\add*siyihlanzile yonke indlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*, lelathi lomnikelo wokutshiswa, lezitsha zalo zonke, letafula lezinkwa zokubukiswa, lezitsha zalo zonke\x + Neh. 13.9.\x*.
\v 19 Lazo zonke izitsha inkosi uAhazi eyayizilahlile ekubuseni kwayo, esiphambekweni sayo, sizilungisile sazingcwelisa, khangela-ke, ziphambi kwelathi leN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 28.24. 1 Lan. 23.28,29.\x*.
\p
\v 20 UHezekhiya inkosi wasevuka ngovivi, wabuthanisa izinduna zomuzi, wenyukela endlini kaJehova.
\v 21 Basebeletha amajongosi ayisikhombisa lenqama eziyisikhombisa lamawundlu ayisikhombisa\x + Ezra 6.17. 8.35.\x* lempongo eziyisikhombisa\x + Ezra 6.17. 8.35.\x*, kwaba ngumnikelo wesono sombuso lesendlu engcwele lesakoJuda\x + Levi 4.14.\x*. Wasesithi emadodaneni kaAroni, abapristi, a\add ku\add*nikele phezu kwelathi leN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 22 Basebehlaba izinkabi, labapristi bemukela igazi balifafaza elathini\x + 35.11. Levi 8.14,15,19,24. Heb. 9.21.\x*; bahlaba lezinqama bafafaza igazi elathini; bahlaba lamawundlu bafafaza igazi elathini.
\v 23 Basebesondeza impongo zomnikelo wesono phambi kwenkosi lebandla, babeka izandla zabo phezu kwazo\x + Levi 4.15.\x*.
\v 24 Abapristi basebezihlaba, benza ukubuyisana ngegazi lazo phezu kwelathi ukwenzela uIsrayeli wonke inhlawulo yokuthula. Ngoba inkosi yalaya: Umnikelo wokutshiswa lomnikelo wesono ngokaIsrayeli wonke\x + Levi 4.26.\x*.
\v 25 Wasebeka amaLevi endlini kaJehova elensimbi ezincencethayo, lezigubhu zezintambo, njalo lamachacho\x + 1 Lan. 16.4. 25.6. 1 Lan. 15.16.\x*, njengomlayo kaDavida\x + 8.14. 1 Lan. 23.5. 25.1.\x* lokaGadi\x + 1 Sam. 22.5.\x* umboni wenkosi\x + 2 Sam. 24.11.\x* lokaNathani umprofethi\x + 2 Sam. 12.1.\x*; ngoba lumlayo wawungesandla sikaJehova ngesandla sabaprofethi bakhe.
\v 26 LamaLevi ema elezinto zokuhlabelela zikaDavida\x + 29.27. 1 Lan. 23.5.\x* labapristi belempondo\x + 1 Lan. 15.24.\x*.
\v 27 UHezekhiya waselaya ukunikela umnikelo wokutshiswa phezu kwelathi; kwathi ngesikhathi umnikelo wokutshiswa uqalisa, ingoma yeN\nd kosi\nd* yaqalisa kanye lezimpondo\x + 1 Lan. 15.24.\x*, langezandla zezinto zokuhlabelela zikaDavida inkosi yakoIsrayeli.
\v 28 Lebandla lonke lakhonza, labahlabeleli bahlabelela, labakhalisi bempondo bakhalisa\x + 1 Lan. 15.24.\x*; konke lokhu, kwaze kwaphela umnikelo wokutshiswa.
\v 29 Lekupheleleni kokunikela inkosi labo bonke abatholakala layo bakhothama bakhonza\x + 20.18.\x*.
\v 30 Khona uHezekhiya inkosi leziphathamandla bathi kumaLevi kawayidumise iN\nd kosi\nd* ngamazwi kaDavida lakaAsafi umboni\x + 2 Sam. 24.11.\x*. Asedumisa kwaze kwaba yintokozo, akhothama akhonza\x + 20.18.\x*.
\v 31 UHezekhiya wasephendula wathi: Selizehlukanisele iN\nd kosi\nd*; sondelani lilethe imihlatshelo leminikelo yokubonga endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 33.16. Levi 7.12.\x*. Ibandla laseliletha imihlatshelo leminikelo yokubonga\x + 33.16. Levi 7.12.\x*, laye wonke olenhliziyo ekhululekileyo, iminikelo yokutshiswa\x + Eks. 35.5,22.\x*.
\v 32 Lenani leminikelo yokutshiswa ibandla elayilethayo lalizinkunzi ezingamatshumi ayisikhombisa, inqama ezilikhulu, amawundlu angamakhulu amabili; konke lokhu kwakungokomnikelo wokutshiswa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 33 Izinto ezazingcwelisiwe kwakuzinkunzi ezingamakhulu ayisithupha lezimvu ezizinkulungwane ezintathu.
\v 34 Kodwa abapristi babebalutshwana, okokuthi babengelakho ukuhlinza yonke iminikelo yokutshiswa; ngakho abafowabo amaLevi babancedisa\x + 35.11. Levi 1.6.\x* waze waphela umsebenzi, labapristi baze bazingcwelisa\x + 30.3,24.\x*, ngoba amaLevi ayeqondile ngenhliziyo kulabapristi ukuzingcwelisa\x + Hlab. 7.10. 125.4.\x*.
\v 35 Leminikelo yokutshiswa layo yayiminengi, lamahwahwa eminikelo yokuthula\x + Levi 3.1,16.\x* kanye leminikelo yokunathwayo yeminikelo yokutshiswa\x + Nani 15.5,7,10.\x*. Ngokunjalo inkonzo yendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd* yamiswa.
\v 36 UHezekhiya labantu bonke basebethokoza ngalokho uNkulunkulu ayekulungisele abantu, ngoba into yahle yenzeka.